rComments: Seems enthused about what she is teaching, but doesn't know how to lecture. Many times i'd look around and see 0 people in the class paying attention regardless of enjoying the material because her lectures are so boring. Exams weren't too bad but relied on knowing things like specific dates, names, etc.

Good prof, but does a decent job at lecturing. She heavily relies on her lecture script which conveys a monotone-like voice resulting in myself trying to stay awake. She's has a bubbly personality outside of class--which doesn't translate to her teaching during class. The deafening silence in the room did not help with the her lecture either.
teacherRatingTags: ['Graded by few things', 'Get ready to read']
